{"word":"ἀναρρώννυμι","slug":"ἀναρρώννυμι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀναρρώννυμι</b></el> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to strengthen afresh</i>:— <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <i>to regain strength</i>, <el>ἀναρρωσθέντες</el>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a> in aor1 <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <i>to recover</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}